            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1696855824799-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has browned, add the <strong>sliced onion </strong>and<strong> sliced mushrooms </strong>to the pan with a very generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until the onion is starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1680278000704-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1680278000704-x400.jpg",
